  "3054710": {
    "name": "Tree Simulator 2.0: Director’s Cut – Leaf Me Alone Edition",
    "steam_appid": 3054710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/4e82cdea461a5dfef09eededa89174e9.poster.avif?t=1765311750\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/4e82cdea461a5dfef09eededa89174e9.webm?t=1765311750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/4e82cdea461a5dfef09eededa89174e9.mp4?t=1765311750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款幽默独特的模拟游戏中，你将扮演一位不同寻常的主角--一棵树！在城市中漫游，体验自由移动的乐趣，探索根植于你的世界。但这还不是全部。作为一棵树，你可以制造混乱，以全新的方式影响周围的环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>在霸王龙杰弗里面前成为一棵树</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杰弗里独自生活，因此脾气暴躁。杰弗瑞讨厌没有效果的植物，因此会攻击它们，这就是典型的杰弗瑞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/a658def0f4d79c6be5ecf2216cb7fba5.poster.avif?t=1765311750\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/a658def0f4d79c6be5ecf2216cb7fba5.webm?t=1765311750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/a658def0f4d79c6be5ecf2216cb7fba5.mp4?t=1765311750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>作为一棵树永垂不朽</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在纪念碑上留下名字，赢得作为一棵树永垂不朽的机会。只有真正的树才能进入坟墓。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/85e0580417d75d36e190a1b496c855ed.poster.avif?t=1765311750\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/85e0580417d75d36e190a1b496c855ed.webm?t=1765311750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054710/extras/85e0580417d75d36e190a1b496c855ed.mp4?t=1765311750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演示版的特点  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为一棵树</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一座城市</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扔人、扔车还是不扔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎接各种活动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎接树恐龙？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >观看松鼠制作 “脏脏的丁当”</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攀爬房屋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多...... 更多...... </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好将这座城市连根拔起了吗？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为一棵树，成为 “树”。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 保加利亚语, 芬兰语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 荷兰语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 瑞典语, 捷克语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 匈牙利语, 韩语, 简体中文",
